<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="en"><head>	<meta charset="UTF-8">	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">	<title>P49</title>	<!-- Bootstrap CSS -->	<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">	<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons/font/bootstrap-icons.css">	<!-- Include jsPDF and html2canvas -->	<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/html2canvas/1.4.1/html2canvas.min.js"></script>	<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jspdf/2.5.1/jspdf.umd.min.js"></script>	<style>		@@page {			size: A4;			margin: 20mm;		}		/* Print styles */		@@media print {			body {				background-color: #fff;			}		}		th, td {			border: 1px solid black;			padding: 8px;			text-align: left;		}		body {			font-family: 'Cambria Math';			margin: 20px;			padding: 0;			background-color: #f8f9fa;		}		.container-box {			max-width: 900px;			background: white;			border: 2px solid #000;			padding: 20px;			box-shadow: 5px 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);		}		.header-table {			width: 100%;			border-collapse: collapse;			margin-bottom: 20px;		}			.header-table td {				border: 1px solid #000;				padding: 8px;				text-align: left;			}		.title {			font-size: 20px;			font-weight: bold;			background: #ddd;		}		td {			border: 1px solid black;			padding: 8px;			text-align: left;			vertical-align: middle;		}		th {			text-align: center;			border: 1px solid black;			padding: 8px;			vertical-align: middle;			word-break: break-word;			white-space: normal;			overflow-wrap: break-word;		}		.company-title {			font-size: 20px;			font-weight: bold;			letter-spacing: 1px;			white-space: nowrap;			word-spacing: 5px;		}		h1 {			font-size: 24px;			font-weight: bold;		}		h2 {			font-size: 18px;			font-weight: bold;		}		.underline {			text-decoration: underline;		}	</style></head><body>	<!-- Close Button -->	<a asp-area="MST_Company" id="top-logo" asp-controller="MST_Company" asp-action="CompanyDetail" class="btn btn-link position-absolute top-0 end-0 m-3 text-dark">		<i class="bi bi-x-lg fs-4"></i>	</a>	<button id="downloadPdf" class="btn btn-primary my-3">Download PDF</button>	<div class="container my-5" id="pdf-content">		<div class="container-box mx-auto p-4">			<table class="header-table">				<tr>					<td class="company-title" colspan="2">QUALITY MANUAL</td>					<td class="company-title" colspan="2">BLIZZARD CERAMICA LLP</td>				</tr>				<tr>					<td colspan="2">SUBJECT : Table of contents</td>					<td>Edition No. : 01</td>				</tr>				<tr>					<td colspan="2">Standard : ISO 9001 : 2015</td>					<td>Rev. No. & Date : 01 / 01.08.2024</td>				</tr>				<tr>					<td colspan="3">Page No. : 49 of 79</td>				</tr>			</table>			<div class="content">				<h1 class="text-center"></h1>				<div class="section">					<p>The documents used in the organization are identified. This is important as all decisions regarding quality management systems are in respect to such maintain documented information. The documents Information are drawing, quality plan, lists, charts, work-instructions, special type of retain documented information etc.  documents also refer to formats / registers to documents where applicable.</p>					<p><strong>FORMATS:</strong></p>					<p>The effectiveness of system is measured by verifying the formats for all functions. The details about the same are defined in procedure / activity chart. Applicable formats are generated as an objective evidence of the activity being carried out.</p>				</div>			</div>			<div class="content">				<h1 class="text-center"></h1>				<div class="section">					<strong>CONTROL OF DOCUMENTS :</strong>					<ol>						<li>All the documented information used in the quality management systems are prepared in accordance to the requirement of the standard ISO 9021-2015.</li>						<li>The documented information are reviewed and approved for adequacy by approving authority prior to issue.</li>						<li>All documented information used in the quality management system are identified by unique numbering & stamp and ensured that all documents are legible.</li>						<li>The documented information are preserved or maintained in electronic media, the same is ensured to have restricted access by the way of password to ensure the misuse by unauthorized person.</li>						<li>All external origin documented information (specification / standards), which are used in the quality management system, are identified and their distributions are controlled. These documented information are verified for the conformance of revision / issue status.</li>					</ol>				</div>			</div>			<div class="content">				<div class="section">					<strong>Reference  :</strong>					<ol>						<li>Procedure For Documented Information    		PC MR 02</li>					</ol>				</div>			</div>			<table class="header-table">				<tr>					<td style="width:35%; height:5vh;"></td>					<td style="width:35%; height:5vh;"></td>					<td rowspan="2"></td>				</tr>				<tr>					<td class="text-center">Prepared By </td>					<td class="text-center">Approved By</td>				</tr>			</table>		</div>	</div>	<script>		document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", () => {			document.getElementById("downloadPdf").addEventListener("click", () => {				const { jsPDF } = window.jspdf;				const pdf = new jsPDF("p", "mm", "a4");				// Get elements to hide				const btn = document.getElementById("downloadPdf");				const logo = document.getElementById("top-logo");				// Temporarily hide elements				if (btn) btn.style.display = "none";				if (logo) logo.style.display = "none";				html2canvas(document.getElementById("pdf-content")).then(canvas => {					const imgData = canvas.toDataURL("image/png");					const imgWidth = 190; // A4 width in mm					const imgHeight = (canvas.height * imgWidth) / canvas.width;					pdf.addImage(imgData, "PNG", 10, 10, imgWidth, imgHeight);					pdf.save("QM_P49.pdf");					// Restore elements after PDF is generated					if (btn) btn.style.display = "block";					if (logo) logo.style.display = "block";				});			});		});	</script></body></html>